= Usage = 

Depending on JNAerator-runtime :

{{{

	<dependency>
	  <groupId>com.jnaerator</groupId>

	  <version>0.9-SNAPSHOT</version>
	  <scope>compile</scope>
	</dependency>
  </dependencies>
}}}
